      <title>特朗普说有多种方法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/trump-won-t-rule-out-seeking-third-term-says-there-are-ways</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他不会排除在白宫寻求第三任期，他在周日的电话采访中告诉NBC新闻，“有一些方法可以让他这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/trump-won-t-rule-out-seeking-third-term-says-there-are-ways</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 16:36:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃尔沃（Volvo）汽车将萨缪尔森（Samuelsson）担任首席执行官两年期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/volvo-car-brings-back-hakan-samuelsson-as-ceo-for-two-year-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔沃汽车AB表示，哈克恩·萨缪尔森（Hakan Samuelsson）于2012年至2022年担任首席执行官，他将夺回舵手，因为瑞典汽车制造商试图导航其迫在眉睫的美国关税，使其摆脱困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/volvo-car-brings-back-hakan-samuelsson-as-ceo-for-two-year-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 15:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普以对普京的愤怒而威胁俄罗斯石油处罚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/trump-says-he-s-very-angry-with-putin-threatens-oil-penalties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他对俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）感到“生气”，如果无法达到乌克兰的停火，他将考虑对俄罗斯石油的“次要关税”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/trump-says-he-s-very-angry-with-putin-threatens-oil-penalties</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 14:40:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着投票的临近，Poilievre悬而未决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/poilievre-dangles-more-invest-in-canada-tax-breaks-as-vote-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党领导人皮埃尔·波利夫（Pierre Poilievre）承诺，如果加拿大的资产销售收益进行了再投资，则将废除资本利得税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/poilievre-dangles-more-invest-in-canada-tax-breaks-as-vote-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 13:34:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗说，它拒绝了我们直接的谈判，以回答特朗普的信</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/iran-says-it-rejects-direct-us-talks-in-reply-to-trump-s-letter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在电视转播的言论中说，伊朗·特朗普（Donald Trump）不会与他的政府进行直接谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/iran-says-it-rejects-direct-us-talks-in-reply-to-trump-s-letter</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 12:00:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥将法官送上小径首次大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/mexico-sends-judges-on-the-trail-for-first-popular-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥选民首次将在周日开始的竞选活动中选举其法官，这一过程涉及数千名鲜为人知的候选人，这些候选人可能会大大改变该国的权力平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/mexico-sends-judges-on-the-trail-for-first-popular-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸叛军随着地震死亡人数升起而呼吁停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/myanmar-rebels-plan-ceasefire-in-quake-hit-areas-as-aid-arrives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸的叛军宣布在地震地区停火，以允许援助到达灾难的受害者，因为巨大的temblor的死亡人数升至约1,700。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/myanmar-rebels-plan-ceasefire-in-quake-hit-areas-as-aid-arrives</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 03:40:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，他希望新的关税将买家送往美国汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/trump-tells-nbc-he-couldn-t-care-less-about-higher-auto-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，如果汽车制造商筹集价格，他希望消费者迁移到美国制造的汽车上，以应对他发誓要强加的所有进口车辆和零件的25％关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/trump-tells-nbc-he-couldn-t-care-less-about-higher-auto-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 23:21:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶鲁大学，哈佛随着特朗普增加压力，哈佛撤离了员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/yale-harvard-remove-employees-as-trump-adds-pressure-to-schools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[耶鲁大学和哈佛大学将雇员从职位上撤职，因为特朗普政府向大学施加压力，要求在校园内与反犹太主义打击或失去联邦资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/yale-harvard-remove-employees-as-trump-adds-pressure-to-schools</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 12:31:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸抵抗宣布部分停火，以促进救济工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-29/urgent-myanmar-earthquake-death-toll-jumps-to-nearly-700-according-to-government-state-run-media-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曼谷（AP​​）＆Mdash;缅甸的影子国家统一政府周六宣布了一个单方面的部分停火，以促进地震救济工作，该政府宣布了与统治军方的流行斗争。该国因灾难的死亡人数飙升至1,644。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-29/urgent-myanmar-earthquake-death-toll-jumps-to-nearly-700-according-to-government-state-run-media-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 04:19:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
